weighttp
------------------------------------------
Webserver benchmarking tool that supports multithreading

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-3
  libev4-4.22-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.25.0-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-4
  python-2.7.14-1
  waf-1.5.19-2

Canonical website:
  https://redmine.lighttpd.net/projects/weighttp/wiki

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/lighttpd/weighttp/archive/weighttp-0.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack weighttp-0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./weighttp-0.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/weighttp-0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/weighttp-0.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(weighttp)
  /usr/bin/weighttp.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/weighttp.README
  /usr/share/doc/weighttp/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/weighttp/README
  /usr/share/doc/weighttp/TODO

------------------

